name: Prototype Sky Striker Ace - Noir
effect:
1+ monsters, including at least 1 "Sky Striker" monster.
You can only special summon 1 "Prototype Sky Striker Ace - Noir" per turn.
When this card is Special Summoned, you can Special Summon "Sky Striker Ace" monsters from your hand or GY to the zones this card points to.
While this card is on the field, monsters your opponent controls with less ATK than this card have their effects negated. Each time a card or effect is activated, this card gains 100 ATK.
(Quick Effect): When a card or effect is activated: You can send 1 card this card points to from the field to the GY; negate that effect and destroy it.
